strings:
<voice_0x010016DB><se_high>Jessica: Hey there, <hero>!
Long time, no see!
How've you been!?

<voice_0x010016DC><se_high>Jessica: You look pretty well, that's for sure. But how come you haven't visited me in Alexandria?
I've missed you!

<voice_0x010016DD><se_high>Jessica: You know, I was planning to go off and live on my own, but my mother was so worried I ended up settling down back at home.<page>Jessica: I guess the time I spent away from her made us both realise what's truly important to us.
We get on really well now!<page>Jessica: I'm not much of a replacement for my brother, but I decided to stay and look after Alexandria. With everyone's help, of course.

<voice_0x010016E2><se_high>Jessica: But enough of that! Have you heard!?
Apparently Yangus and Red have teamed up now and they're doing something together!<page>Jessica: Can you believe it!? Last I remember, they couldn't exchange two words without three insults! I wonder what went on between them.
<voice_0x010016E3><se_high>Jessica: Huh? You're on your way to pick up Princess Medea? Yeah, I guess it's time to get going.
<voice_0x010016E4><se_high>Jessica: Okay then, I'll be waiting for you down in the courtyard.
<voice_0x010016DD><se_high>Jessica: You know, I was planning to go off and live on my own, but my mother was so worried I ended up settling down back at home.

<voice_0x010016DE><se_high>Jessica: I guess the time I spent away from her made us both realise what's truly important to us.
We get on really well now!
<voice_0x010016DF><se_high>Jessica: I'm not much of a replacement for my brother, but I decided to stay and look after Alexandria. With everyone's help, of course.

<voice_0x010016E0><se_high>Jessica: But enough of that! Have you heard!?
Apparently Yangus and Red have teamed up now and they're doing something together!
<voice_0x010016E1><se_high>Jessica: Can you believe it!? Last I remember, they couldn't exchange two words without three insults! I wonder what went on between them.
